summary: Greg Andersen calls Julie D'Arcane to ask for help with his hacky sacks. The sacks have been up on the balcony since 1988.
suggested_actions: Confirm the date and time of Greg Andersen's visit to retrieve the hacky sacks.
Ensure that the balcony area is accessible and clear for Greg to collect the items.
Follow up with Greg after his visit to confirm that he successfully retrieved the hacky sacks and address any further needs he may have.
